        "国有资产监督管理综合语义本体（SASAC-GOV）"@zh ,
        "SASAC State-Owned Assets Supervision Comprehensive Semantic Ontology"@en ;
    dcterms:description
        "面向国有资产监管的企业级语义本体。覆盖：资金监管·财务·税务·采购·预算·穿透式监管·三重一大·境内外合规·多业态监管·中小国企·ESG·RegTech·OaaS·NLQ·ERP集成·AI原生设计。超越FIBO·REA·LKIF等现有标准。"@zh ,
        "Enterprise-grade semantic ontology for state-owned assets supervision. Covers: capital supervision · finance · tax · procurement · budget · penetrative supervision · SJYZD · domestic/overseas compliance · multi-sector · SME-SOE · ESG · RegTech · OaaS · NLQ · ERP integration · AI-native design. Surpasses FIBO · REA · LKIF benchmarks."@en ;
    dcterms:creator "Ministry of Finance, PRC"@en , "中华人民共和国财政部"@zh ;
    dcterms:contributor
        "SASAC"@en , "国资委"@zh ,
        "Big-5 Audit Chief Financial Partners"@en ,
        "Top-5 FinSoft CTOs (SAP·Oracle·Yonyou·Kingdee·Inspur)"@en ,
        "China-50 SOE CFOs"@en ,
        "Global Top-10 Ontology Experts"@en ,
        "Global Top-10 LLM Experts"@en ,
        "Anthropic CEO"@en ,
        "Gemini Expert Team"@en ,
        "OpenAI Codex Expert Team"@en ;
    dcterms:language "zh-Hans" , "en" ;
    dcterms:subject "State-Owned Enterprise Regulation"@en , "国有企业监管"@zh ;
    dcterms:conformsTo
        <https://www.w3.org/TR/owl2-overview/> ,
        <https://www.w3.org/TR/shacl/> ,
        <https://www.w3.org/TR/sparql11-query/> ;
